{{> layout/header-login}}
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/user-login.css">
<main class="cc-login-main">
    <section class="cc-login-shell">
        <div class="cc-login-form">
            <h1>CatchCatch</h1>
            <p class="cc-login-form__desc">로그인하고<br>다양한 콘서트와 만나요</p>
            {{#errorMessage}}<p class="cc-badge" style="margin-bottom:16px">{{errorMessage}}</p>{{/errorMessage}}
            <form action="/login" method="post">
                {{#_csrf}}<input type="hidden" name="{{parameterName}}" value="{{token}}">{{/_csrf}}
                <div class="cc-input-wrap"><span class="cc-input-icon">✉</span><input class="cc-input" type="text" name="username" placeholder="이메일 또는 아이디" autocomplete="username"></div>
                <div class="cc-input-wrap"><span class="cc-input-icon">🔒</span><input class="cc-input" type="password" name="password" placeholder="비밀번호" autocomplete="current-password"><span class="cc-input-eye">◉</span></div>
                <div class="cc-login-options">
                    <label class="cc-check"><input type="checkbox" name="rememberId"> 아이디 저장</label>
                    <span>보안 접속 ?</span>
                </div>
                <button class="cc-btn cc-btn--primary cc-btn--full" type="submit">로그인</button>
            </form>
            <div class="cc-divider">또는</div>
            <div class="cc-social-row">
                <a class="cc-social cc-social--kakao" href="/oauth2/authorization/kakao">● 카카오로 로그인</a>
                <a class="cc-social cc-social--naver" href="/oauth2/authorization/naver">N 네이버로 로그인</a>
                <a class="cc-social" href="/oauth2/authorization/google">G 구글로 로그인</a>
            </div>
            <div class="cc-login-links">
                <a href="/join">회원가입</a><span>|</span><a href="/find-id">아이디 찾기</a><span>|</span><a href="/find-password">비밀번호 찾기</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <aside class="cc-login-promo" style="--promo-img: url('{{#promoImageUrl}}{{promoImageUrl}}{{/promoImageUrl}}{{^promoImageUrl}}/images/sample/banner-main.svg{{/promoImageUrl}}')">
            <div class="cc-login-promo__content">
                <div>
                    <p>함께하는 순간,<br>잊지 못할 감동</p>
                    <h2>2026 전국투어<br>콘서트 <em>티켓 오픈!</em></h2>
                    <p>지금 CatchCatch에서<br>예매하고 특별한 경험을 즐겨보세요.</p>
                </div>
                <a class="cc-btn cc-btn--primary" href="/concerts">콘서트 둘러보기 →</a>
            </div>
        </aside>
    </section>
</main>
{{> layout/footer}}
